    "div" : "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narrativa gerada: ValueSet canal-autenticacao-biometrica</b></p><a name=\"canal-autenticacao-biometrica\"> </a><a name=\"hccanal-autenticacao-biometrica\"> </a><ul><li>Include estes códigos, tal como definidos em <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-RoleCode.html\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-RoleCode</code></a><span title=\"Version is explicitly stated to be 4.0.0\"> versão &#x1F4CD;4.0.0</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Código</b></td><td><b>Ecrã</b></td><td><b>Definição</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-RoleCode.html#v3-RoleCode-HOSP\">HOSP</a></td><td>Sistema da Operadora (presencial)</td><td>An acute care institution that provides medical, surgical, or psychiatric care and treatment for the sick or the injured.</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-RoleCode.html#v3-RoleCode-PHARM\">PHARM</a></td><td>Sistema do Prestador (presencial)</td><td>Location where healthcare service was delivered, identified as a pharmacy.</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-RoleCode.html#v3-RoleCode-OUTPHARM\">OUTPHARM</a></td><td>Aplicativo da Operadora (teleatendimento)</td><td>**Description:** A location that plays the role of delivering services which may include providing judicious, safe, efficacious, appropriate and cost effective use of medicines for treatment of patients for outpatient visits and may also be used for discharge prescriptions.</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
